Pre-Req’s

Ubuntu <16.0> 
Docker 
Kubeadm
Kubectl
Kubelet


https://medium.com/@dileepjallipalli/setting-up-a-single-master-kubernetes-cluster-on-aws-using-kubeadm-fad03e5937cf

After installing docker configure docker daemon to use systems container’s cgroups

https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/production-environment/container-runtimes/#docker

Then restart docker and enable on boot as follows below. 
